Hindi ba komportable na kasama ako?

00:21:11.500 --> 00:21:13.335
Gusto ko itong makita mismo.

00:21:14.336 --> 00:21:17.255
Kung saan huling naroon si Jae-hee.

00:21:17.339 --> 00:21:20.675
Anong nangyari doon.
