00:26:58.430 --> 00:26:59.848
Sige, sige.

00:27:03.268 --> 00:27:04.436
Hindi ba ikaw si La-ik?

00:27:10.400 --> 00:27:11.359
ANG ABOGADO AY NAGLALARO SA KANILANG

00:27:11.443 --> 00:27:14.070
